  "text": "(a) Cosmic censorship [38] is respected, and hence, the no-bifurcation theorem requires the horizons merge into a single structure [CITATION_1] . (b) The BH uniqueness (\"no-hair\") results [40] [41] [42] [43] together with the apparent stability of the Kerr family of solutions [44] implies the end-state must be a Kerr BH 5 .",
